Usage: readTSVConfig [-help] [-chipName <string>] {[-stackedDieFile <string>][-powerFile <string>][-topNetlist <string>]}

-help                        # Prints out the command usage
-chipName <string>           # name used when current die is instantiated
                             # (string, optional)
-powerFile <string>          # Power Connection file name. (string, optional)
-stackedDieFile <string>     # Stacked Die file name. (string, optional)
-topNetlist <string>         # Top level netlist verilog file name.
                             # (string, optional)